content: I like the sound of Depeche Mode and The Human League, I'll definitely check them out. The jazz recommendations are also intriguing, especially Thundercat and Kamasi Washington. I'll have to give them a listen. By the way, I've been listening to a lot of music on my daily commute, and I've recently discovered a new Spotify playlist called "Retro Electro" which has become my go-to playlist for the morning drive.
